"""
Part 2 — Multi-Sample OES Analyser
=====================================
Loads the reference peaks CSV produced by Part 1, then compares any
number of sample spectra against those peaks.

Features
--------
* Intensity lookup at each reference peak position (with configurable tolerance)
* Integration-time normalisation (reads "NNms" from filenames)
* Vibrational temperature (Tvib) via N2 C→B 0-0 / 1-0 band ratio
* Trend plots: Tvib vs Power (W) and Tvib vs Pressure (mTorr)
* PCA across all samples using the reference-peak intensities as features
  - Score plot coloured by pressure, marker shape for argon %
  - PC1 loadings bar chart to show which peaks drive separation
* Full text results file export
"""

